Text: Phillip WarnickDavid and I wanted to let you know that Phillip has broken his arm over the weekend and he will be out of sports for a while He has an appt with an orthopedic surgeon on Friday and we should know more after that with regards to exactly how long he has to be in a cast Needless to say Phillip is very disappointed We will keep you posted Thanks David and Carolyn Warnick
